Show HN: Not Another CV
text:
Introducing NotAnotherCV.com - The Tool to Tailor Your CV to Your Dream Job

Have you ever sent out your CV and received no response? It can be frustrating to spend time applying for a job and not get a single call back. The problem might be that your CV is too generic and doesn't highlight your skills and experience that match the specific job requirements.

That's where NotAnotherCV.com comes in. It's a CV management tool that lets you create multiple versions of your CV, each tailored to a specific job or company. You can easily customize your CV for each application, highlighting your relevant skills, experiences, and achievements.

This will help you stand out from other candidates, show the hiring manager that you understand their needs, and increase your chances of getting an interview.

With NotAnotherCV.com, you can save time and effort by embedding your CV on your existing website. Allowing hiring managers who come across your website to download you CV and reach out to you.

I've been working on notanothercv.com for a couple of months and it's been reasonably well received but I was pushed to post here. As such I'd appreciate it if you checked it out.
